{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_018NBByWa27GdXojUVYQUMvE","type":"tool_result","content":"# CSS Custom Properties for Dark Button Styling\n\nBased on the token file, here are the relevant properties:\n\n**Primary/Dark Button Background (Light Mode):**\n- `--primary: #6F2DBD` (violet purple)\n- `--primary-foreground: oklch(0.985 0 0)` (near white text)\n\n**Dark Mode Equivalent:**\n- `--primary: oklch(0.985 0 0)` (inverted to white/light)\n- `--primary-foreground: oklch(0.16 0.015 270)` (dark text)\n\n**For a #333-like Dark Background:**\nThe closest match is `--background` in dark mode: `oklch(0.16 0.015 270)`, which represents a very dark gray-blue tone suitable for dark interfaces.\n\nThe design uses a violet primary color (`#6F2DBD`) that inverts between light and dark themes, with the dark mode background providing the deep neutral tone typically associated with `#333`."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"5a57d822-e398-4198-9dc4-ceadd30199eb","uuid":"df65ca34-1dec-403e-9ef9-62c8d0ea014b","timestamp":"2026-07-18T14:51:40.804Z","tool_use_result":{"bytes":2104,"code":200,"codeText":"OK","result":"# CSS Custom Properties for Dark Button Styling\n\nBased on the token file, here are the relevant properties:\n\n**Primary/Dark Button Background (Light Mode):**\n- `--primary: #6F2DBD` (violet purple)\n- `--primary-foreground: oklch(0.985 0 0)` (near white text)\n\n**Dark Mode Equivalent:**\n- `--primary: oklch(0.985 0 0)` (inverted to white/light)\n- `--primary-foreground: oklch(0.16 0.015 270)` (dark text)\n\n**For a #333-like Dark Background:**\nThe closest match is `--background` in dark mode: `oklch(0.16 0.015 270)`, which represents a very dark gray-blue tone suitable for dark interfaces.\n\nThe design uses a violet primary color (`#6F2DBD`) that inverts between light and dark themes, with the dark mode background providing the deep neutral tone typically associated with `#333`.","durationMs":3810,"url":"https://ui.askewly.com/llms/tokens/tokens.css"}}
